                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">San
                                        Salvador</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1908-11-09"><hi rend="italic">November 9,
                                1908</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>William Adler sailed from Puerto Cortes November 3 by steamer <hi rend="italic">Ellis</hi>, destination New Orleans.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Dodge.</hi></signed></closer>
